2. Canvera Digitial Technologies Pvt. Ltd.

Project 1 : Interactive Pricing Catalogue - Canvera is an online photography company which provides mass customized printed products, Photo Books albums, e-commerce solutions for customers as well as photographers.This product is used to give the cost estimate of the product. Various options are provided where the user can choose and customize the product and it will show the estimated cost for that.

Project 2 : Get listed photographer app - This product was aimed for the photographers to create their profiles on canvera.com. Few of the features in this product include, creation of profile, managing the profile after creation. The photographer can showcase his work by uploading photos and videos captured by him. He can also apply for any of the photography jobs related to him among a few others.
Project 3 : Get listed consumer app - This product was an extension to get listed app which was aimed at reaching out to general consumers. Few features of this app included the consumers to view their activity, get in touch with the photographers via chat in web, get notifications about various activities like the status of their job, messages sent by the photographer to name a few.

Project 4 : Get Listed Admin Web application (Canvera Internal product) - This is an internal product used by the canvera team to keep track of newly registered users from    http://photographers.canvera.com. This application shows the listing of all the users whose profile has been published and unpublished . Few features of this product include, approving/rejecting the content posted by the photographer in their profile. Once the changes have been verified by the team it is then published which will then reflect in their main profile page. In addition to that, it also has a feature to create new profile of a photographer by the customer care team.

Project 5 : Photostory Admin Web application (Canvera Internal product) - This product is used for creating photostories. Few features of this app include, uploading the images for a special occasion and converting the same into a narrated story. The story is split into various chapters which is dynamic. Each chapter has various functionalities like uploading images, previewing the photostory. It also has a listing page which has all the list of photostories created wherein you can perform CRUD operations.

Project 6 : Photostory - This is end product of what has been created in photostory admin. This has various themes under different categories like Weddings,Babies & Kids, Nature among others. The themes uses Parallax which gives a smooth feel to the end product and includes features like sharing of photostory as well. 

Project 7 : Canvera Blog - This is done using popular CMS, Wordpress. The theme is customized as per the design given by the designers.

Project 8 : Emailer - Email templates which are sent to the customer.
